<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2589066>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Male habitus of Trigonidium solis sp. nov. in dorsal (A) and lateral (B) views. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2589066/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2589072>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Trigonidium solis sp. nov. female: dorsal habitus (A), head and pronotum in lateral view (B), subgenital plate in ventral view (C), abdominal apex and ovipositor in lateral view (D). Scale bars: 1 mm (A, B, D), 0.5 mm (C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2589072/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2589068>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Trigonidium solis sp. nov. male: face in anterior view (A), first abdominal tergite (absence of metanotal gland and hind wing) in dorsal view (B), abdominal apex in dorsal (C) and ventral (D) views. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2589068/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2589070>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Trigonidium solis sp. nov. male genitalia of the holotype (A) and paratype (B). Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
